### Get all latest prices
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prices-latest

### Get latest price for BTCUSDT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prices-latest/BTCUSDT

### Get latest price for ETHUSDT
GET http://localhost:8080/api/prices-latest/ETHUSDT

### Get wallet balance
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wallet/1

### Get trade history
GET http://localhost:8080/api/trades/1

### BUY 0.01 BTC
POST http://localhost:8080/api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "side": "BUY",
  "quantity": 0.01
}

### SELL 0.01 BTC
POST http://localhost:8080/api/trade
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "symbol": "BTCUSDT",
  "side": "SELL",
  "quantity": 0.01
}

